<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> bevor. Als du uns
                                <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hast von Veits,
                                <expan>münczmeist<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<add>czü Lawffe</add>, deins <expan>brüd<ex>er</ex>s</expan>,
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, darumb <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Haller, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, cze rede gesaczt, wan
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Teczel selig vorlangst
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> todes <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>abgange<ex>n</ex></expan> ist; und hat uns
                            <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Hall<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, wie vor czeiten, des nu bey vier und
                        czweinczig <expan>jare<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Veit mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>derbt</expan> würd; und das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        er noch <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Teczel nicht getan, sunder in sprech ein
                                <expan>münczmeist<ex>er</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Erlang<ex>en</ex></expan> an; und des Veits habe
                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>wünd</expan> sich weilunt
                                <expan>selig<ex>er</ex></expan> gedechtnüzz des
                                <expan>hochg<ex>eporn</ex></expan>
<expan>fürst<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Fridrichs gewalt
                            <expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Abemsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, der desmals sein
                            <expan>viczt<ex>um</ex></expan> czü Sulczbach
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>. Dewcht dich <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                        daz <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> czü <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Haller
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> des Teczels
                            <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, icht czu sprechen hest, darumb
                                <expan>wöll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir dir <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> scheinboten mit
                            <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> vollen gewalt
                                <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>slewnige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> hellffen, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim sind; und bedarffst du
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> geleits darczu, daz wöllen wir dir
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> geben; und getrawen dir wol, du laszt
                        dich daran von <add>den</add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> benügen und darüber dich nicht beclagest.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Mich<ex>ahelis</ex></expan>.</ab>
